   "source": [
    "4. The string \"Howl's Moving Castle\" is a correct value. Why isn't the single quote character in the word Howl's\n",
    "    not escaped a problem?"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "id": "11464332",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Ans:- The single quote in Howl's is fine because you've used double quotes to mark the beginning and \n",
    "        end of the string. like wise we can use double quotes in with single quotes"
   ]
  },
  {
